Scripts to run on the public meta-server (in a screen session)

Build pioneers with:
$ autogen.sh --prefix=/home/pioneers/local
$ make all install

Start screen
$ screen -c screenrc

In screen 0 "meta": The local meta-server (./meta.sh)
In screen 1 "local lobby": The local lobby (./locallobby.sh)
In screen 2 "local lobbybot": The local lobbybot (./locallobbybot.sh)
In screen 3 "remote lobby": The remote lobby (./remotelobby.sh)
In screen 4 "remote lobbybot": The remote lobbybot (./remotelobbybot.sh)

Other scripts:
list.sh
	Show all running games

kill-game.sh [port]
	Kill a game running on the given port

getVersions.sh
	Show the version in various distributions (whohas is better...)

